Operation Syntax Addition <code>a+b</code> Subtraction <code>a-b</code> Multiplication <code>a*b</code> Division <code>a/b</code> Modulo <code>a%b</code> <p>Refer to the Mathematical Operations section of this guide for useful mathematical functions.</p> <p>Unary Negative</p> <p>There is no unary negative operator in XS</p> <pre><code>void main() {
    int a = 10;

    // this does not work:
    int b = -a+20;

    // instead use:
    int b = 0-a+20;
}
</code></pre>
